      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a precision Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis maintains factory-spec rigidity with zero subframe fatigue, while the dual-VANOS system has been meticulously maintained for optimal valve timing and torque delivery. Power is transferred through a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional lateral grip and corner-exit traction. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing lightweight aluminum control arms and a perfectly damped multi-link rear setup. This is a mechanically flawless specimen with an unblemished aesthetic, representing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance.",
